cs.GT, cs.CE, cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.AI

The paper focuses on the application of game theoretic methods to energy trading, which falls under the category of game theory (cs.GT). It also involves the use of optimization techniques and control theory, which are subfields of computational engineering (cs.CE) and systems and control (cs.SY), respectively. Machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI) are also relevant due to the use of predictive models and decision-making algorithms.
